Text: RE Location Number Cc Kevin I just forwarded the data for the locations to Frank for review He is currently in a meeting However I did not see any reference to a Gomez pipe in those locations Mary Original Message From Hyatt Kevin Sent Wednesday February AM To Hubbard Mary Cc Carriere Frank Subject RE Location Number Importance High I have a meeting with the customer Thursday morning is it possible to have an answer by this afternoon Original Message From Hubbard Mary Sent Tuesday February PM To Hyatt Kevin Subject RE Location Number Kevin Its been a busy morning Ill look these up ASAP Mary Original Message From Hyatt Kevin Sent Tuesday February AM To Carriere Frank Hubbard Mary Subject RE Location Number Importance High I found these numbers in a file Loc Code Im not sure what assets they are in reference to kh Original Message From Carriere Frank Sent Tuesday February AM To Hyatt Kevin Subject FW Location Number FYI As I indicated in my phone message we are not finding these assets using the description provided Judy Beck is or was the facilitiy person for ETS She is now Dynegy therefore we may get a referral instead of an answer Original Message From Hubbard Mary Sent Friday February PM To Carriere Frank Subject FW Location Number FYI Original Message From Hubbard Mary Sent Friday February PM To Subject Location Number Judy I need to provide a NBV for a Gomez Laterial miles of pipe to Kevin Hyatt Frank says it should be in company TW I ran the following locations numbers but found nothing in co Can you help Thanks Mary I
